title: L'armure de Jade
overview: Jade is a legendary superhero. And now it's up to Lan Jun to wear her armor... hard to believe it's her turn to don the famous Jade armor and use her kung fu skills to fight evil! With the help of her friends, Theo and Alisha, as well as the Beasticons, the legendary servants of the armor, Lan Jun must fight against super villains and manage her teenage life.
